{
  "stem": "1684.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 303.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, I came into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[CRYING] The Gestapo came in again, and I had to go into hiding with my cousins where I went, because I couldn't go into our apartment anymore.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was like a ghost town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was completely like-- I didn't look in the mirror, but everybody told me I looked like I came from the grave after the eight days.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we were saved again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now we worked for Madritsch [CRYING] till Goeth came-- Goeth came home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[CRYING] [DRINKS] Madritsch and Goeth-- Goeth was the oberscharfuhrer from Plaszow in Krakow, where all the Krakow people worked already.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now Madritsch wanted to open up a company there, in-- in-- in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So because the ghetto had to be liquidated-- they had two ghettos in the meantime, an A ghetto and a B ghetto.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We worked--we were the working ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then there was the A ghetto for the-- for the-- for the old people and for the children.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had to-- the 1st of-- the 2nd of September, my husband's birthday, I remember that-- my husband's birthday, at 6 o'clock in the morning, the ghetto was-- everybody was-- like-- they came, and we had to go out to the appellplatz there.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Goeth came, and he had everything for us by companies.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were working for Madritsch, and the ghetto was supposed to be liquidated.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were taken out to the trains, to the-- you know, to the cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we're taking 105 people in one car.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were taken to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when we came to Plaszow, it was just in the evening.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there were big, big-- we didn't eat anything from the morning, 6 o'clock, til the next evening, we didn't have anything.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
